'''Conjunctivitis''' (also known as '''pinkeye''') is a [[medical]] condition when the ''Conjunctiva'' (a [[transparent]] [[membrane]] that lines the outer [[eye]], and inner part of the [[eyelid]]) becomes [[infection|inflamed]]. The cause of conjunctivitis can be either [[bacteria]]l or [[Virus|viral]] infection.

